{"tid":1484072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[家庭教育的重要] 支持家長遊行帶小朋友出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:22:47.000Z","uid":236593,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f80a63407dfd083eee2f1c78dc894fb7a67d3de","tid":1484072,"uid":236593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"今日喺銅鑼灣行街發夢，忽然好大雨，有一家四口同我一齊避雨... <br />\n<br />\n個妹妹喊到眼又腫 面又紅<br />\n真係陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正想遞上紙巾之際，就聽到以下對話:<br />\n<br />\n媽:呢度無police, 好安全架<br />\n妹:(繼續喊) <br />\n媽:啲哥哥姐姐叫口號就好似sports day咁叫啲朋友加油囉！唔洗驚架！<br />\n我地都叫番聲加油好唔好？<br />\n妹:加... 加油<br />\n媽:(一邊開益力多一邊講) 拿！頭先啲哥哥姐姐請你飲益力多，佢地都好乖，police先會打人同拉人架咋<br />\n<br />\n之後，我同小朋友high five加油 <br />\n目送呢一家四口離開<br />\n<br />\n仲聽到個媽媽話<br />\n我地一齊保護香港，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係好撚感動呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n完全係身教嘅典範！望到呢個媽媽，我見到佢身上發緊光！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港加油！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02005c7c169dfdfb68378c6f4341f9b11067e2c0","tid":1484072,"uid":236593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11bd38fe819e7f96a9176d664fc64bea8989755b","tid":1484072,"uid":236593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f22150b7af80142a94ff3f969369c50f7f0502bf","tid":1484072,"uid":276633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e94040c0d5816b2f1f25a9c5d48d745532ea81","tid":1484072,"uid":275752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差"},{"pid":"c0c4ff7e87a4a3fb22c9efc4c27f80e7d694eedb","tid":1484072,"uid":236593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e94040c0d5816b2f1f25a9c5d